songs.title: Rock wit U
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
There's no escape on the spell you have placed
Leaving my heart and my mind
Foolish am I if I was to try
To ever leave you behind

[Chorus]
I wanna rock wit u, come give me all your love
No matter what we do, I wanna rock wit u
Wit u and wit only u, I wanna rock wit u
I wanna rock wit u, rock wit you, baby

[Verse 2]
I'll stay and walk this life wit u
No matter what we may go through
Dead broke, no job, no house, no ride
I'm gonna stay right by your side

[Chorus]
I wanna rock wit u, come give me all your love
No matter what we do, I wanna rock wit u
Wit u and wit only u, I wanna rock wit u
I wanna rock wit u, rock wit you, baby, baby

[Bridge]
Don't question where you're headed to, my love
Don't be afraid, just believe in love

[Chorus]
I wanna rock wit u
No matter what we do
Wit u and only u
I wanna rock wit u
I wanna rock wit u
No matter what we do
Wit u and only u
I wanna rock wit u
I wanna rock wit u
No matter what we do
Wit u and only u
I wanna rock wit u

[Outro]
Do your thing, do your thing
Do your thing, do your thing
Do your thing, do your thing
Do your thing, do your thing
Do your thing, do your thing
Do your thing, do your thing
Do your thing, do your thing
Do your thing, do your thing
